modName: Skyrim Radioactive Glorified - Interiors Compilation and Undeath Compatability Patch
descriptionHtml:
This small patch fixes issues in the Winking Skeever when Undeath and Skyrim Radioactive Glorified - Interiors Compilation are used together.

Fixes:

Puts back a section of wall in the cellar that Undeath removes
Restores a few statics removed by Undeath
Restores the Solitude Sewers entrance in the cellar

Requires:

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/77269/?]Skyrim Radioactive Glorified - Interiors Compilation[/url]
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/40607/?]Undeath
[/url]
Load Order:

Skyrim Radioactive - Interiors Compilation.esp
Undeath.esp
Skyrim Radioactive Interiors Compilation - Undeath Patch.esp
